  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (5 days, Commercial, Office renovation)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Info:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Salary: Basic up to $4500</strong></li><li><strong>Working Hour: Monday - Friday (9am - 6pm)</strong></li><li><strong>Location: Bendemeer MRT</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Review construction drawings and prepare quantity take-offs.</li><li>Analyse costs for maintenance and additional works.</li><li>Source, evaluate, and compare quotations from suppliers and subcontractors.</li><li>Negotiate costs and terms with contractors and subcontractors.</li><li>Maintain proper documentation for tenders and procurement activities.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Civil/Quantity Surveying/Building/Construction or equivalent</li><li><strong>Minimum 1 years of QS experience in office renovation / interior design QS.</strong></li></ul><p><em><strong></strong></em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em></p><p>People Profilers Pte Ltd, 20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building, Singapore 049705</p><p>Tel: 6950 9744</p><p>So Boon Shyen, Debbie</p><p>EA Licence Number: 02C4944</p><p>Registration Number: R1111376</p>",
